{% comment %}
  ShipBoost — Free Shipping Progress Bar (app embed).

  Enabled once in Theme Settings → App embeds. Renders site-wide (target: body)
  so "Display On" (All / Home / Product / Cart / Product+Cart) works on every
  page without the merchant adding a block to each template. The extension JS
  then relocates the bar to the chosen Position (or below the header for "None").

  Uses the same shared snippet as the section block, so both render identically.
  The section block remains available and unchanged for merchants who prefer to
  place the bar in a specific section — the JS renders only one bar if both exist.
{% endcomment %}
{% render 'ship-boost-bar' %}

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "ShipBoost Progress Bar",
  "target": "body",
  "stylesheet": "ship-boost-progress-bar.css",
  "javascript": "ship-boost-progress-bar.js",
  "settings": []
}
{% endschema %}
